title: Total Researcher Growth and Numbers, Select Countries throughout Europe, 2001 to 2006
name: Total Researcher Growth and Numbers, Select Countries throughout Europe, 2001 to 2006
description:
This dataset shows select countries in Europe and their percentage change in growth in the number of researchers in the country from 2001 to 2006. 

These figures will give a good indication on which countries throughout Europe are making strides in promoting a research friendly environment.

Data fields with a -1 represent no data available
